---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Christophe Trefois" description="Learn more about Christophe Trefois - technology leader, data infrastructure expert, and AI innovation champion.">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="section">
      <div class="about-header">
        <div class="profile-photo">
          <img src="/christophe-trefois.jpg" alt="Christophe Trefois" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="section-title">Dr. Christophe Trefois</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="flex-col">
          <div class="card">
            <h2>Professional Background</h2>
            <p>
              I am currently the <strong>Head of Technology at the Luxembourg National Data Service (LNDS)</strong> 
              (<a href="https://lnds.lu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">lnds.lu</a>), 
              a position I've held since November 2022. In this role, I lead the technology team responsible for 
              building and operating the infrastructure and tools that enable secure, FAIR (Findable, Accessible, 
              Interoperable, Reusable) data sharing across Luxembourg's public and private sectors.
            </p>
            <p>
              At LNDS, I oversee the development of critical data infrastructure including secure processing environments, 
              data cataloguing systems, pseudonymization services, and federated data access platforms. My team of data 
              engineers, software engineers, DevOps specialists, and security experts works on enabling value creation 
              from secondary use of data while ensuring data protection by design and default. We actively contribute to 
              European initiatives including the <a href="https://health.ec.europa.eu/ehealth-digital-health-and-care/european-health-data-space_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">European Health Data Space</a> and support Luxembourg's participation in 
              cross-border data collaboration projects.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2>Research Interests</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning Infrastructure</li>
              <li>Large-scale Data Infrastructure & Management</li>
              <li>Genomic Data Infrastructure & Federated Systems</li>
              <li>Data Governance & GDPR Compliance</li>
              <li>Reproducible Research & Open Science</li>
              <li>High-Performance Computing & Cloud Platforms</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="card">
            <h2>Education</h2>
            <div class="edu-item">
              <h3>PhD in Systems Biology</h3>
              <p><strong>University of Luxembourg, LCSB</strong></p>
              <p class="meta">2010 - 2014 | <a href="https://www.uni.lu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">uni.lu</a></p>
              <p>Developed computational approaches for understanding disease progression and cellular responses 
              to perturbations, with focus on Parkinson's disease.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="edu-item">
              <h3>MSc in Communication Systems (Dipl.-Ing.)</h3>
              <p><strong>EPFL (École Polytechnique Fédérale de Lausanne)</strong></p>
              <p class="meta">2008 | <a href="https://www.epfl.ch" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">epfl.ch</a></p>
              <p>Master thesis on "Secure Integration of Wireless Sensor Networks into Applications" 
              conducted at SAP Labs France.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card mt-lg">
            <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
            <div class="timeline">
              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2022 - Present</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                  <h4>Head of Technology</h4>
                  <p>Luxembourg National Data Service (LNDS)</p>
                  <p class="timeline-link">
                    <a href="https://lnds.lu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">lnds.lu</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2020 - Present</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                  <h4>Member</h4>
                  <p>National Ethics Committee (CNE)</p>
                  <p class="timeline-link">
                    <a href="https://cne.public.lu/fr.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">Commission Nationale d'Éthique</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2017 - Present</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                  <h4>Deputy Technical Coordinator</h4>
                  <p>ELIXIR Luxembourg</p>
                  <p class="timeline-link">
                    Luxembourg Centre for Systems Biomedicine (LCSB) | 
                    <a href="https://elixir-luxembourg.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">elixir-luxembourg.org</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2014 - 2022</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                  <h4>Team Leader for Responsible and Reproducible Research</h4>
                  <p>Bioinformatics Core, Luxembourg Centre for Systems Biomedicine (LCSB)</p>
                  <p class="timeline-link">
                    <a href="https://wwwen.uni.lu/lcsb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="primary-link">wwwen.uni.lu/lcsb</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2011</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                  <h4>Visiting Researcher</h4>
                  <p>Institute for Systems Biology (ISB), Seattle</p>
                  <p class="timeline-link">
                    Labs of Dr. David Galas and Dr. Adrian Ozinsky
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2008 - 2010</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                  <h4>IT Consultant & IT Auditor</h4>
                  <p>Ernst & Young Luxembourg</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Skills & Expertise</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Technical Leadership</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Team management & mentoring</li>
            <li>Strategic technology planning</li>
            <li>Infrastructure architecture</li>
            <li>Project coordination</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Bioinformatics & Data Science</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Systems biology modeling</li>
            <li>Genomics & transcriptomics</li>
            <li>Data integration pipelines</li>
            <li>Statistical analysis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Software & Tools</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Julia, Python, R</li>
            <li>HPC & cloud computing</li>
            <li>Docker, Kubernetes</li>
            <li>Git, CI/CD pipelines</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Data Management</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>FAIR data principles</li>
            <li>Metadata standards</li>
            <li>Data stewardship</li>
            <li>Database design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Compliance & Governance</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>GDPR implementation</li>
            <li>Data privacy frameworks</li>
            <li>Consent management</li>
            <li>IT auditing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Conference organization</li>
            <li>Scientific reviewing</li>
            <li>Workshop facilitation</li>
            <li>Open source contribution</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Connect With Me</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        I'm always interested in discussing technology, research collaborations, and innovative projects in bioinformatics and data science.
      </p>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .profile-photo img {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -2.375rem;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-bg);
  }

  .timeline-date {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
  }

  .placeholder-text {
    background-color: #fef3c7;
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #92400e;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .dark .placeholder-text {
    background-color: #451a03;
    color: #fbbf24;
    border-left-color: #f59e0b;
  }
</style>
